The water pipe was carried out about 40 years ago during the last repair.
At the same time they made us a small kitchen in a back and a toilet from a former closet.
We live exactly where Demidov and his family lived, and the servants lived on the second floor.
Our apartment is not privatized, and why?
The Ufa Real Estate Center says privatization doesn't matter.
We still get only a one-room apartment, we can not claim more.
Four months ago they promised to resettle us, but it did not go beyond promises.
I'm not used to complaining, and I won't.
In this apartment (room!) lived a whole dynasty: my grandparents, mother and dad, me and my husband and my daughter with a granddaughter.
